instance.name: Heaven-on-High (Floors 61-70)
instance.description: After vanquishing the monstrous guardian Hiruko, you finally learn the truth of Heaven–on–High. Constructed millennia ago by the Onishishu, it serves as a proving ground for warriors that may one day deliver the world from calamity. Your instincts as an adventurer spur you onwards and upwards as you strive for the very top of the tower.
